1
00:00:11,830 --> 00:00:12,830
You...

2
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:17,070
will all be buried with me.

3
00:00:39,390 --> 00:00:41,120
This is the antidote for Ricin.

4
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:42,820
I'll give you a choice.

5
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,430
An assassin just broke in

6
00:01:02,430 --> 00:01:03,750
and triggered the Bird Alarm Bell.

7
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:05,150
The assassin is now dead.

8
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:06,300
Stand down!

9
00:01:11,789 --> 00:01:12,350
Wait!

10
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:13,750
Leave the assassin's body here

11
00:01:13,750 --> 00:01:15,950
for His Majesty to verify his identity!

12
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:37,710
Xing?

13
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:46,680
Xing,

14
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:47,920
it's me.

15
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:51,350
Zhuge Yue...

16
00:03:20,810 --> 00:03:26,070
[REBIRTH]

17
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:29,100
[Episode 26]

18
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,930
Pass on my order!

19
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,710
Everyone retreat outside the inner palace.

20
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,510
Any trespassers will be killed!

21
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,520
All guards!

22
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,190
His Majesty is unwell.

23
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,670
All guards are ordered to retreat
out of the inner palace courtyard!

24
00:03:51,670 --> 00:03:52,630
No trespassing!

25
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:53,340
Yes!

26
00:04:06,010 --> 00:04:07,610
Hurry up and check how she is.

27
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:12,190
No vital organs were hit.

28
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,450
She is just exhausted.

29
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,560
I will go get some medicine to save her.

30
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,090
Alright.

31
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,560
We can only force-feed her the medicine
for now.

32
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,270
If it works,

33
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:40,220
she will wake up in a couple of days.

34
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,390
You go rest first.

35
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,260
The poison in your body...

36
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,120
I am fine.

37
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,080
Xing!

38
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,360
Just lie down and don't move around.

39
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:30,720
Don't die
before General Chu actually dies.

40
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,850
I wouldn't know how to explain it to her
when she wakes up.

41
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:37,240
What is this?

42
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,450
If I'm not mistaken,

43
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,870
this is the antidote to Blood on Snow.

44
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,120
When I was looking for medicine
for General Chu,

45
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,380
I found it by accident.

46
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,520
This smell...

47
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,270
It's wolf vine?

48
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,680
Exactly. It's wolf vine from Ximeng.

49
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,600
It is highly toxic,

50
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,750
but it counteracts Blood on Snow.

51
00:05:56,770 --> 00:05:58,430
So it can be used
to fight poison with poison,

52
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,750
and force Blood on Snow

53
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,410
out of your heart completely.

54
00:06:02,410 --> 00:06:03,310
It's just that...

55
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:05,190
It's just that wolf vine is highly toxic.

56
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,520
It could be an antidote
or a deadly poison.

57
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,680
Not only that,

58
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,870
besides wolf vine,

59
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:12,600
there are other herbs in it
whose origin I don't know.

60
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,070
But given the toxicity of wolf vine,

61
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:16,000
you'll likely fall into a coma
for 7 days after taking it,

62
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,360
with a continuous fever
during the whole time.

63
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,160
If the fever subsides on its own,

64
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,900
you will wake up within 7 days.

65
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,870
If it doesn't...

66
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,240
If it doesn't, you can have my corpse

67
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,300
for your research.

68
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:27,630
I...

69
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,580
Well...

70
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:29,870
Really?

71
00:06:33,230 --> 00:06:34,159
What about Xing?

72
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,430
How is she?

73
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:37,240
She's fine.

74
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,360
I checked her injuries.

75
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:38,980
There's nothing serious.

76
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:39,960
She is just exhausted.

77
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,870
She will wake up in a couple of days
after taking medicine.

78
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:42,630
I've already asked Meng En

79
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,630
to bring Minglu and Wang Shi'er

80
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,430
over here.

81
00:06:44,450 --> 00:06:46,250
Minglu is looking after her now.

82
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,830
I'll go see her.

83
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,180
What about the medicine?

84
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,980
I'll take it after Xing wakes up.

85
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,750
Xing,

86
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,530
since you left Qingshan Manor,

87
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,480
we have had many misunderstandings

88
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:22,020
and almost been separated
by life and death.

89
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,360
I can't remember how long it has been

90
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:29,360
since I looked at you this closely.

91
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:36,530
I always thought
there was no danger in the world

92
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,800
that could not be resolved.

93
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,780
Now, being with you like this,

94
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,480
I am afraid.

95
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:49,440
I'm afraid I can't make it
until you wake up.

96
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:56,560
I'm afraid that this time,

97
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,320
death will truly separate us.

98
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,480
My Lord.

99
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:14,000
My Lord?

100
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,480
Miss Chu's breathing has been steady
these past few days.

101
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,680
She is out of danger.

102
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:23,270
My Lord, please drink this medicine first.

103
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,870
This smell...

104
00:08:27,420 --> 00:08:28,740
It smells bad,

105
00:08:28,770 --> 00:08:30,300
but it's my newly developed decoction.

106
00:08:30,300 --> 00:08:33,559
It can temporarily suppress
the Blood on Snow in your body.

107
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,030
Rest assured, Young Master.

108
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,830
Miss Chu will certainly be fine.

109
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,360
Why did she pass out so quickly?

110
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,890
Did I use too much medicine?

111
00:09:13,070 --> 00:09:14,190
You sneaky rat!

112
00:09:14,210 --> 00:09:16,440
You don't even make a sound when you walk?

113
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,640
It's just a habit
I've developed from work.

114
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,440
Loud noises might wake the dead.

115
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:20,180
Well...

116
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:22,980
Lord Zhuge has had a fever for 3 days.

117
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:25,320
Aren't you afraid he won't wake up?

118
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,120
He will surely die without the medicine.

119
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,840
Taking it gives him a ray of hope.

120
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,750
I am a miracle doctor
with noble medical ethics,

121
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,000
almost like the reincarnation
of the divine physician Hua Tuo.

122
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,530
How could I leave him to die?

123
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,750
Right.

124
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,790
You are the reincarnation
of legendary doctors.

125
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,600
But just in case—

126
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,440
if he doesn't wake up,

127
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:45,750
how will you explain it to Lady Chu?

128
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,600
Then I can only hope

129
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:51,120
that either they both wake up,

130
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:52,600
or...

131
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,720
neither of them wakes up.

132
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,530
What are you muttering about?

133
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,660
Reaching the same end
by different means...

134
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,960
isn't a bad thing!

135
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,960
Bad news!

136
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,150
Something...

137
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,870
Something terrible happened to Miss Chu!

138
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:06,720
Miss Chu?

139
00:10:06,870 --> 00:10:08,480
Miss Chu... Miss Chu...

140
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,000
Tell us!

141
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,750
She woke up!

142
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,700
She woke up?

143
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,150
How did it happen so fast?

144
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,390
You didn't tell her

145
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:17,320
about Young Master Zhuge, did you?

146
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,360
Lady Chu...

147
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,120
Xiao Ran.

148
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,080
Hurry up and check his pulse.

149
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,740
His pulse doesn't seem right.

150
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,510
Minglu,

151
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,640
fetch me a basin of colder water.

152
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,600
What are you waiting for?

153
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:47,870
♪ The dust in the world ♪

154
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:51,630
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

155
00:10:52,570 --> 00:10:55,360
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

156
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,390
♪ And not be scared? ♪

157
00:10:57,570 --> 00:10:59,590
♪ A slight ripple ♪

158
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:03,360
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

159
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:07,010
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

160
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:10,600
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

161
00:11:11,490 --> 00:11:14,860
♪ Let it be ♪

162
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:19,370
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

163
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:22,750
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

164
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:24,690
♪ Go weaving ♪

165
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:30,150
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

166
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:33,460
♪ We once beheld ♪

167
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:36,890
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

168
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:41,140
♪ Beauty never ♪

169
00:11:41,170 --> 00:11:45,900
♪ Lasts for long ♪

170
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:49,720
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

171
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:54,180
♪ It's just a stone ♪

172
00:11:54,560 --> 00:12:01,770
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

173
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:01,200
How is he?

174
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,870
It's been 7 days.

175
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:06,080
His pulse is chaotic, and the high fever
still hasn't gone down.

176
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,870
It should be caused
by the heat poison of Blood on Snow.

177
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,790
The heat poison is fierce.

178
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,510
If it can't be released,

179
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:11,120
it will coagulate inside his body.

180
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:13,390
Then it will be even harder for him
to wake up.

181
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,440
Is there any way?

182
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,480
The fastest way to cool him down

183
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,550
is to soak his whole body in ice water.

184
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,120
Miss Chu,

185
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,040
everything is ready.

186
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:49,640
Tell them to leave.

187
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,100
Yes.

188
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:41,180
♪ On the water ♪

189
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,910
♪ Countless ♪

190
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:44,620
♪ Ripples rise ♪

191
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:49,220
♪ Through the mortal world ♪

192
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:52,680
♪ With meetings and goodbyes ♪

193
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:56,970
♪ How unfair fate is ♪

194
00:13:56,990 --> 00:14:01,990
♪ It gave all the memories back to you ♪

195
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,850
♪ Yet left me ♪

196
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:07,460
♪ Stuck right here ♪

197
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:08,000
Xing,

198
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:09,150
you are...

199
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:10,810
♪ Rain falls down ♪

200
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:13,630
an invincible... general.

201
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,560
♪ Lingering thoughts ♪

202
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:15,560
♪ Awake once more ♪

203
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:17,080
You can definitely...

204
00:14:17,050 --> 00:14:19,230
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

205
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:23,120
♪ Another me ♪

206
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,670
take me away.

207
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,510
I know you are still alive,

208
00:14:25,050 --> 00:14:27,050
♪ How can I escape ♪

209
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,960
and I know it was you
who sent the Huotu water.

210
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:31,840
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

211
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:31,030
Zhuge Yue,

212
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,550
you've been alive all along.

213
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:35,440
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

214
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:36,280
Why have you been hiding from me?

215
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:39,060
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

216
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,600
Since you chose this path yourself,

217
00:14:39,090 --> 00:14:43,510
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

218
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,480
even if it leads through
a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood,

219
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,790
you will walk it alone.

220
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,440
But if one day,

221
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:47,300
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

222
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:47,160
you find you can no longer
take a step forward,

223
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,360
you know the way...

224
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:49,740
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

225
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:51,480
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

226
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,170
back to Qingshan Manor.

227
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:54,110
♪ Searching for your name ♪

228
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:58,910
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

229
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,940
You've always been protecting me.

230
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:02,820
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

231
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,510
Now,

232
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,000
it's my turn to protect you.

233
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,840
♪ Melt the ice ♪

234
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,870
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

235
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,200
Zhuge Yue,

236
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,480
you told me

237
00:15:06,890 --> 00:15:12,100
♪ Let the night ♪

238
00:15:07,870 --> 00:15:09,330
that if one day I regret it,

239
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,670
you would be right behind me,

240
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:12,000
waiting for me to return.

241
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:12,800
You can't die.

242
00:15:13,450 --> 00:15:18,770
♪ Forever glow ♪

243
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,880
You must always be here.

244
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:15,840
I promise you.

245
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:18,710
I want you to stay by my side forever too.

246
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,450
To the ends of the earth,

247
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,520
we live and die together.

248
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:37,200
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

249
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:40,990
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

250
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,440
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

251
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:45,180
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

252
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,800
♪ Searching for your name ♪

253
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:52,610
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

254
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,960
They're the Sun-Moon Twin Swords.

255
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:56,520
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

256
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:54,750
They represent

257
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,240
that we will be together forever.

258
00:15:56,540 --> 00:15:58,540
♪ Melt the ice ♪

259
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:00,560
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

260
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:05,800
♪ Let the night ♪

261
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:12,460
♪ Forever glow ♪

262
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:23,770
[Capital of Great Yan]

263
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:06,349
Keep going.

264
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,310
We are almost home.

265
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:11,589
Keep going. Be good.

266
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:15,200
Let's go.

267
00:17:47,080 --> 00:17:48,710
Helian, are you alright?

268
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:53,930
Take me to see His Majesty.

269
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,480
General Cheng, thank you

270
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:00,270
for sending people to search for me

271
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:02,310
during the turbulent times in Great Yan.

272
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,510
This is His Majesty's order.

273
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:04,840
I was just following it.

274
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:13,580
Thanks for your trouble, General Cheng.

275
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:28,720
Your Majesty!

276
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:29,790
What is it?

277
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,160
Your Majesty,

278
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:33,010
Consort Helian has returned.

279
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:38,000
I see.

280
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,490
I'm glad she's back safely.

281
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:42,560
Tell her to go back and rest.

282
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,640
You may leave too.

283
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,200
Yes.

284
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:47,350
Your Majesty!

285
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,170
Your Highness!

286
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,240
Your Majesty!

287
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,810
No need to pay respects.

288
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,720
I'm glad you're back safely.

289
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,640
I rushed back to the Capital of Great Yan
day and night

290
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,970
because I have something to report to you.

291
00:19:11,380 --> 00:19:12,450
Sister Huan!

292
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:14,720
Sister Huan, there's a letter for you!

293
00:19:14,890 --> 00:19:16,160
Sister Huan!

294
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:17,560
There's a letter for you!

295
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,550
Sister Huan. Sister Huan.

296
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:23,240
There's a letter for you.

297
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:23,960
There's a letter for you.

298
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,720
Thank you.

299
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:29,070
Buy yourself some fruits.

300
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:33,830
I want it too! I want it too!

301
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,400
Go on. Buy yourselves some fruits.

302
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,240
Let's go buy some fruits.

303
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:40,480
Okay, let's go!

304
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:41,070
Let's go!

305
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,070
Take care.

306
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:56,680
As a token of gratitude

307
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,920
for the donkey.

308
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:04,390
[I will repay your kindness
for lending me the donkey.]

309
00:20:06,450 --> 00:20:07,820
It's you?

310
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,200
Jing,

311
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,880
take the troops away.

312
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:05,400
Don't disturb the villagers.

313
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:05,920
Yes!

314
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:10,450
Your Majesty, please rest early.

315
00:22:12,050 --> 00:22:14,420
We will camp here tonight.

316
00:22:15,750 --> 00:22:16,400
Yes.

317
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,500
Do you remember it?

318
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:11,180
This is Mountain Snow.

319
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:16,160
This...

320
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:18,110
is Mountain Snow?

321
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:20,480
This was my father's favorite horse.

322
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:23,240
Once, I secretly rode it out.

323
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:25,640
It got spooked,

324
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:27,880
broke off its reins, and ran away.

325
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,310
Afraid of my father's punishment,

326
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:31,000
I didn't dare to return to the palace.

327
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:31,920
It was you

328
00:23:32,270 --> 00:23:34,870
who looked for it with me
all night in Mount Hei.

329
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:38,110
We found it by the Li River in the end.

330
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:40,200
What exactly are you trying to say?

331
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,110
You once told me

332
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,960
that making mistakes doesn't matter.

333
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:47,130
As long as you make amends in time,

334
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,440
it's never too late.

335
00:23:51,790 --> 00:23:52,480
Huan Huan,

336
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,640
I lost Great Yan.

337
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,460
Can you help me get it back?

338
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:06,160
You must have already known the reason

339
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:10,960
I invited you elders here today.

340
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:17,720
You'll be deciding

341
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:20,720
where the future of Great Yan lies.

342
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:23,110
We will follow the old rules.

343
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:25,400
Each of you has an eagle feather arrow.

344
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,550
Putting it in the upper censer
means you agree

345
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:30,640
that the 13 tribes
will secede from Great Yan,

346
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:33,240
govern themselves, and form an alliance.

347
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,550
Otherwise,

348
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,110
it means you veto it.

349
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:45,070
Except for the Yan family,

350
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:49,440
the elders of the 12 tribes are all here.

351
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:50,960
Please,

352
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:53,720
after careful consideration,

353
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,350
cast your vote.

354
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:02,480
This horse is not Mountain Snow at all.

355
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:04,410
Four years ago, I rode it on a hunt.

356
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:05,790
To protect me,

357
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:09,090
it was killed by ferocious wildcats.

358
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,620
What are you trying to say?

359
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:15,030
Even the horses in Great Yan
know how to repay a favor.

360
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,360
I won't give you a chance

361
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,070
to kill me again.

362
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:26,750
Elders, what are your decisions?

363
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:30,310
Great Yan is already beset
by internal and external troubles.

364
00:25:30,310 --> 00:25:32,400
The new King of Great Yan
is not up to the task.

365
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:34,440
If you cannot see the stakes here,

366
00:25:34,910 --> 00:25:37,000
you can only wait for your doom.

367
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:41,800
Is the Snowy Region Tribe still
going to sit back and do nothing?

368
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:45,200
Boy,

369
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,410
do you remember how your sister

370
00:25:47,510 --> 00:25:49,200
was killed?

371
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:05,880
Our Snowy Region Tribe
made an alliance with the Yan family

372
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,540
to protect Great Yan forever,

373
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:09,030
and protect the King of Great Yan.

374
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:11,030
I cannot break my father's promise.

375
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,960
What your father
promised the old King of Great Yan

376
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:16,270
was to protect Great Yan,

377
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:17,790
not Yan Xun's family!

378
00:26:18,130 --> 00:26:19,470
Only by making the right choice

379
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:20,790
for your tribe

380
00:26:20,990 --> 00:26:22,120
are you truly

381
00:26:22,310 --> 00:26:24,110
keeping your father's promise!

382
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:34,510
An Luo.

383
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,000
General Huan?

384
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,020
General Huan is not dead?

385
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:44,820
Sister?

386
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,520
General Huan?

387
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:53,240
Sister!

388
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:55,850
I thought you...

389
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,330
I thought you...

390
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:04,390
Your Majesty?

391
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:05,190
Your Majesty!

392
00:27:14,650 --> 00:27:15,890
Your Majesty.

393
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:17,070
Your Majesty.

394
00:27:23,130 --> 00:27:24,040
Well done.

395
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,470
You are the pride
of our Snowy Region Tribe.

396
00:27:40,790 --> 00:27:41,590
General Huan.

397
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:45,480
You have been away from Great Yan
for a long time.

398
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,550
You have no idea

399
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:47,930
what Great Yan has gone through

400
00:27:47,930 --> 00:27:49,000
during this time.

401
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:50,420
I'm afraid you can't vote

402
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:52,880
on behalf of the Snowy Region Tribe now.

403
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:53,590
Besides,

404
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,830
don't you think you should tell us

405
00:27:55,830 --> 00:27:57,310
where you have been these days

406
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:59,720
and what happened?

407
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,830
Elder Huo Sang.

408
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,310
Back then,
Great Yan had just opened up trade.

409
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:06,440
A Great Yong supply caravan
was plundered in the Baichuan Tribe.

410
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,640
The Emperor of Great Yong was furious

411
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:08,790
and sent troops to demand an explanation.

412
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:10,830
If it wasn't the old King of Great Yan
who mediated the matter...

413
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:12,640
As someone who experienced it back then,

414
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:15,510
Elder Huo Sang,
you must still remember it vividly.

415
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,000
Elder Pale.

416
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:21,160
Do you know how,
during those extremely cold years,

417
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:22,790
when you were forced to migrate south

418
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:24,310
with no food or clothing,

419
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,550
you eventually found

420
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,960
this fertile land?

421
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:28,840
Oh, right.

422
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:31,440
Elder Tubu.

423
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,070
Do you still remember

424
00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:34,920
who overcame all objections

425
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:37,830
to dig a canal
from the other side of Mount Huihui

426
00:28:37,830 --> 00:28:39,440
to bring fresh water
to the Hongchuan Tribe?

427
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,900
Everything you mentioned

428
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:43,030
was done by the old King of Great Yan.

429
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:45,590
The old King of Great Yan
was indeed kind to us,

430
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:47,680
but we have also served him loyally
all our lives.

431
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:50,310
Now Great Yan is torn apart

432
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:52,810
and can't withstand any more storms.

433
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:53,510
Are you

434
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:56,200
asking us, for this so-called loyalty,

435
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:59,080
to completely ignore
the fate of Great Yan?

436
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:10,920
Now, surrounded by tigers and wolves,

437
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:13,110
the winter of Great Yan is approaching.

438
00:29:13,110 --> 00:29:16,000
If the 13 tribes fall apart,

439
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:18,310
Great Yan will no longer exist!

440
00:29:32,750 --> 00:29:33,920
This arrow

441
00:29:34,750 --> 00:29:37,480
was made by my father
with his own hands back then.

442
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:40,720
I've been keeping it with me
all these years

443
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:42,380
and never let it leave my side.

444
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:44,680
My previous actions

445
00:29:45,590 --> 00:29:46,790
have failed Great Yan

446
00:29:48,110 --> 00:29:49,400
and failed my father.

447
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:51,720
But I believe,

448
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,480
if he were here today,

449
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:58,620
he wouldn't want to see Great Yan
fall apart.

450
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:04,010
So I'm casting this vote

451
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,400
for my father.

452
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,110
Huan Huan,

453
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,750
the winter of Great Yan is approaching.

454
00:31:17,750 --> 00:31:20,160
The 13 tribes will survive
if we stay together.

455
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,550
If we fall apart,

456
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:24,440
Great Yan will no longer exist.

457
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,550
I once thought

458
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:33,440
the Snowy Region Tribe and Great Yan
would share the same fate.

459
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:35,640
I am your subject and relative,

460
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,730
and I should be loyal to you.

461
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,070
But after facing death once,

462
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:41,920
I understand now.

463
00:31:44,590 --> 00:31:46,790
I won't be blindly loyal to you anymore.

464
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,940
I will return to Great Yan.

465
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,640
That is my home.

466
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,240
However,

467
00:31:56,350 --> 00:31:58,550
I want 5,000 Black Eagle Army soldiers.

468
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:01,120
They must be under my command completely.

469
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:25,160
In today's Ximeng,

470
00:32:25,830 --> 00:32:27,030
all people are equal!

471
00:32:27,110 --> 00:32:28,170
Long live the King!

472
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:29,790
Long live the Queen!

473
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:32,130
I am no longer a noble young master
of the Zhuge family.

474
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:35,440
I can only cling to you and marry into
the Chu family as your matrilocal husband.

475
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:36,920
By order of His Majesty!

476
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:38,550
The Seventh Prince
mobilized troops without permission.

477
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:40,110
He is suspected
of colluding with the enemy to rebel.

478
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:41,590
The Painting of the Subjugated Queen!

479
00:32:41,590 --> 00:32:42,680
Today,

480
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,720
I will trample on

481
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:46,510
Yan Xun's dignity.
